## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Transition style between strips**: When the video moves from one webtoon strip (page) to the next, should it:
> - **Hard cut** (instant switch) — simplest, most common in recap videos
> - **Cross-dissolve** (0.3s fade) — smoother but adds complexity
> - **Matched scroll** (exit bottom of strip A → enter top of strip B as continuous scroll) — most immersive but technically complex
>
> Current pipeline uses hard cuts between clips. Recommend keeping hard cuts for now, adding cross-dissolve as a future enhancement.

> [!NOTE]  
> **Scale height tuning**: The upscale target (3000px) may need adjustment based on testing. Higher = better quality at high zoom but slower FFmpeg processing. We can make this configurable via `detailPresets.js`.
